    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>This video will be showcasing the Customer database, including:</p><ul><li><p>Adding new customers</p></li><li><p>Managing\u00a0existing customers</p></li><li><p>Marketing List exports</p></li></ul><a class=\"external-link\" data-card-appearance=\"embed\" data-layout=\"center\" data-original-height=\"480.00\" data-original-width=\"853.34\" data-width=\"100.00\" href=\"https://youtu.be/r0022CKGJPM\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://youtu.be/r0022CKGJPM</a><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Control - f79824.png\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1936654474/Control%20-%20f79824.png?api=v2\"></span><h3 id=\"CustomerManagementResources(withVideo)-CustomerProfileManagement\">Customer Profile Management</h3><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933344786/Creating+a+Customer+Profile\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933344786\" data-linked-resource-version=\"9\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Creating a Customer Profile</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1933312070/Managing+Customer+Profiles\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1933312070\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Managing Customer Profiles</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/plugins/servlet/servicedesk/customer/confluence/shim/spaces/SCD/pages/1933246632\" rel=\"nofollow\">Customer Management: Importing Customer Data</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/plugins/servlet/servicedesk/customer/confluence/shim/spaces/SCD/pages/1931116664\" rel=\"nofollow\">Customer Ticket and Device History</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/plugins/servlet/servicedesk/customer/confluence/shim/spaces/SCD/pages/1933541687\" rel=\"nofollow\">Adjusting Credit Balances</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/plugins/servlet/servicedesk/customer/confluence/shim/spaces/SCD/pages/1933869089\" rel=\"nofollow\">Required Fields for Customer Profiles</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/plugins/servlet/servicedesk/customer/confluence/shim/spaces/SCD/pages/2036891839\" rel=\"nofollow\">Zip Code Validation for Customers</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/plugins/servlet/servicedesk/customer/confluence/shim/spaces/SCD/pages/1932394664\" rel=\"nofollow\">Assigning a Customer Referral Source</a></p><h3 id=\"CustomerManagementResources(withVideo)-CustomerMarketing\">Customer Marketing</h3><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/plugins/servlet/servicedesk/customer/confluence/shim/spaces/SCD/pages/1933803749\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reports: Marketing List</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/plugins/servlet/servicedesk/customer/confluence/shim/spaces/SCD/pages/1932361859\" rel=\"nofollow\">Integration Setup: Revv/Rallio</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933803609\" rel=\"nofollow\">Integrations: Twilio</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/plugins/servlet/servicedesk/customer/confluence/shim/spaces/SCD/pages/1937014890\" rel=\"nofollow\">Automating Customer Lists to Mailchimp through Zapier</a></p><h3 id=\"CustomerManagementResources(withVideo)-NotificationsandReceipts\">Notifications and Receipts</h3><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/plugins/servlet/servicedesk/customer/confluence/shim/spaces/SCD/pages/1933246465\" rel=\"nofollow\">Automated Notifications Resources</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933803736\" rel=\"nofollow\">Send an SMS Ticket Status Notification</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2767290399\" rel=\"nofollow\">Create an Automated SMS Notification</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2816507905\" rel=\"nofollow\">Create an Automated Email Notification</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1933672639\" rel=\"nofollow\">Email a Receipt to a Customer</a></p><h3 id=\"CustomerManagementResources(withVideo)-CustomerAppointments\">Customer Appointments</h3><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/plugins/servlet/servicedesk/customer/confluence/shim/spaces/SCD/pages/1934491696\" rel=\"nofollow\">Appointments Overview</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/plugins/servlet/servicedesk/customer/confluence/shim/spaces/SCD/pages/1934786625\" rel=\"nofollow\">Appointments: Viewing Set Appointments</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/plugins/servlet/servicedesk/customer/confluence/shim/spaces/SCD/pages/1934917649\" rel=\"nofollow\">Appointments: Scheduling an Appointment</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/plugins/servlet/servicedesk/customer/confluence/shim/spaces/SCD/pages/1934852150\" rel=\"nofollow\">Appointments: Changing an Appointment</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/plugins/servlet/servicedesk/customer/confluence/shim/spaces/SCD/pages/1934491709\" rel=\"nofollow\">Appointments: Canceling an Appointment</a></p><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/plugins/servlet/servicedesk/customer/confluence/shim/spaces/SCD/pages/1933246822\" rel=\"nofollow\">Appointment General Settings</a></p><p>\u00a0</p><p /><p> </p><p />",
